// Hotkey Conversion Batch 1
// Converting first 3 hotkeys from HotkeyManager.cpp to Havel language scripts

// 1. Mode toggle (Ctrl+Alt+G)
// Original: ^!g => mode.toggle()
^!g => mode.toggle()

// 2. Reload configuration (Ctrl+Alt+R)  
// Original: ^!r => config.reload()
^!r => config.reload()

// 3. Quit application (Alt+Esc)
// Original: !Esc => exit()
!Esc => exit()